OL,3,CSearch launched for 'specialist and
OL,4,Cworthy' design team for Grenfell
OL,5,Cmemorial
OL,7,FAn international search has begun for
OL,8,Fa "specialist and worthy" team to
OL,9,Fdesign a memorial for the site of
OL,10,FGrenfell Tower.
OL,12,FRepresentatives from the local
OL,13,Fcommunity in west London said the
OL,14,Flaunch of the selection process means
OL,15,Fthe vision for a permanent marker of
OL,16,Fwhat happened is "a significant step
OL,17,Fcloser".
OL,26,@pD@COUpD@YO]xD@ROUyD@GO]
