OL,3,CSearch launched for 'specialist and
OL,4,Cworthy' design team for Grenfell
OL,5,Cmemorial
OL,7,FThe 72 people who died in the June
OL,8,F2017 blaze deserve nothing less than a
OL,9,F"beautiful and lasting memorial", they
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,FThe aim is to have a final design team
OL,13,Fselected and announced in spring next
OL,14,Fyear, with hopes that a planning
OL,15,Fapplication could be made in 2027 ` 10
OL,16,Fyears on from the fire.
OL,18,FThe search for a team has been
OL,19,Flaunched by the Grenfell Tower
OL,20,FMemorial Commission with the Royal
OL,21,FInstitute of British Architects (RIBA).
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@`O]
