OL,4,Cworthy' design team for Grenfell
OL,5,Cmemorial
OL,7,FThe commission said the intention is
OL,8,Fto "create a significant, reflective
OL,9,Fand impactful memorial" to commemorate
OL,10,Fwhat happened "and express the love we
OL,11,Fhave for those we have lost and will
OL,12,Fremember forever".
OL,26,@pD@DOUqD@WO]rD@OOUtD@QO]
