OL,3,CSearch launched for 'specialist and
OL,4,Cworthy' design team for Grenfell
OL,5,Cmemorial
OL,7,FThe first part of the selection phase
OL,8,Fis not expected to result in a fixed
OL,9,For final design proposal, it added,
OL,10,Fsaying it is firstly "crucial to find
OL,11,Fa team with the best people who can
OL,12,Fadopt a sensitive and inspiring design
OL,13,Fapproach" while working with the
OL,14,Fcommunity to develop an "early
OL,15,Fconcept".
OL,17,FA report from the commission last year
OL,18,Fset out a series of recommendations
OL,19,Ffor a "sacred space" designed to be a
OL,20,F"peaceful place for remembering and
OL,21,Freflecting".
