OL,4,Cworthy' design team for Grenfell
OL,5,Cmemorial
OL,7,FIt said the space should include a
OL,8,Fgarden, a monument and a dedicated
OL,9,Fspace for the private expression of
OL,10,Fgrief and mourning for the families
OL,11,Fwho lost loved ones.
OL,13,FViews on the use of parts of the tower
OL,14,Fin any lasting memorial were mixed,
OL,15,Fthe commission said, with some people
OL,16,Ffeeling they "should form part of the
OL,17,Fmemorial" while "others do not agree".
OL,26,@xD@NOUyD@IO]yD@QOUyD@eO]
