OL,3,CSearch launched for 'specialist and
OL,4,Cworthy' design team for Grenfell
OL,5,Cmemorial
OL,7,FThe commission recognised it was
OL,8,F"hugely difficult area with many
OL,9,Fdifferent views" and said it will
OL,10,F"work through how we can respect the
OL,11,Fsensitivities on all sides".
OL,13,FThe commission has also previously
OL,14,Facknowledged that an exact timeline
OL,15,Ffor developing the memorial depends on
OL,16,Foutside factors including the
OL,17,FGovernment's decision on the future of
OL,18,Fthe tower, which remains standing with
OL,19,Fa green heart at the top.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@PO]rD@AOUsD@[O]
