OL,3,CSearch launched for 'specialist and
OL,4,Cworthy' design team for Grenfell
OL,5,Cmemorial
OL,7,FIn a joint statement, the commission's
OL,8,F10 community representatives, said:
OL,9,F"Launching the memorial design team
OL,10,Fselection process brings us a
OL,11,Fsignificant step closer to turning the
OL,12,FGrenfell community's memorial vision
OL,13,Finto a physical reality.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
