OL,3,CSearch launched for 'specialist and
OL,4,Cworthy' design team for Grenfell
OL,5,Cmemorial
OL,7,F"Through this process, we intend to
OL,8,Fidentify and appoint a specialist and
OL,9,Fworthy design team. A team that has
OL,10,Fproven experience of working on
OL,11,Fsensitive and community-focused
OL,12,Fprojects, and who can clearly
OL,13,Fdemonstrate the integrity with which
OL,14,Fthey will approach this vital task.
OL,16,F"The beautiful and lasting memorial to
OL,17,Four 72 loved ones deserves nothing
OL,18,Fless."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOUzD@FO]
