OL,3,CSearch launched for 'specialist and
OL,4,Cworthy' design team for Grenfell
OL,5,Cmemorial
OL,7,FCommission co-chairs Thelma Stober and
OL,8,FLord Paul Boateng said: "Our primary
OL,9,Fcommitment as the commission is to
OL,10,Festablish a dignified and peaceful
OL,11,Fspace for the Grenfell community to
OL,12,Fcommemorate.
OL,14,F"And our fundamental pledge, from the
OL,15,Foutset, has been to prioritise the
OL,16,Fvoices and wishes of the entire
OL,17,FGrenfell community in the decision-
OL,18,Fmaking process, both now and in the
OL,19,Ffuture."
OL,26,@pD@YOUvD@AOU{D@HO]
