OL,3,CSearch launched for 'specialist and
OL,4,Cworthy' design team for Grenfell
OL,5,Cmemorial
OL,7,FJane Duncan, RIBA's competitions
OL,8,Farchitect adviser, said the design
OL,9,Fprocess will be "a huge challenge" and
OL,10,Fit will be "a tricky task" to find the
OL,11,Fright team who can "draw upon their
OL,12,Fdeepest streams of empathy and
OL,13,Fdelicacy".
OL,15,FShe said: "This incredible and unique
OL,16,Fdesign team selection process sits
OL,17,Fnaturally on an international stage,
OL,18,Fjust as the tragedy resonated far
OL,19,Facross the globe.
