OL,4,Cworthy' design team for Grenfell
OL,5,Cmemorial
OL,7,F"I ask all architects and designers,
OL,8,Fwherever you may be, to consider if
OL,9,Fyou have the right skills and
OL,10,Fexperience in dealing with many and
OL,11,Fdiverse stakeholders, in sensitivity
OL,12,Fof approach and compassion, as well as
OL,13,Fthe innovation and creativity to
OL,14,Finterpret and deliver a wonderful
OL,15,Fdesign to meet a very personal and
OL,16,Ftouching brief."
OL,18,FMore information at is available at
OL,19,Fwww.grenfelltowermemorial.co.uk/design
